Really?

12
00:01:51,658 --> 00:01:52,624
You're going to Nanjing?

13
00:01:52,659 --> 00:01:54,354
Yeah. Two days before my wedding.

14
00:01:55,262 --> 00:01:56,729
I'd say that calls for a drink.

15
00:01:57,531 --> 00:01:59,624
- Okay.
- Maybe I can help your plans along.

16
00:01:59,866 --> 00:02:00,855
All right.

17
