19
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,120
Not ours.

20
00:02:20,155 --> 00:02:21,120
Barnes!

21
00:02:21,555 --> 00:02:23,288
This is my good friend Andy..

22
00:02:23,323 --> 00:02:25,325
Fisher.
