just don't know it yet.

82
00:05:39,085 --> 00:05:40,954
The papers say we're
both from the States.

83
00:05:40,989 --> 00:05:42,251
So try and talk American.

84
00:05:42,589 --> 00:05:43,556
Of course, old chap.

85
00:05:51,731 --> 00:05:54,427
We're carrying Red Cross supplies..

86
