97
00:07:08,443 --> 00:07:09,397
Okay.

98
00:07:15,215 --> 00:07:16,182
Good luck, Eddie.

99
00:11:44,117 --> 00:11:45,084
Get me the cigarette.

100
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,726
You are safe now.

101
00:11:57,263 --> 00:11:58,230
