106
00:12:11,778 --> 00:12:14,180
Nobody but a journalist
would walk into Nanjing

107
00:12:14,215 --> 00:12:16,080
armed with nothing but a sports coat.

108
00:12:16,449 --> 00:12:18,818
The enemy's patrol team is
six streets away from us.

109
00:12:18,853 --> 00:12:19,817
What is this place?

110
00:12:19,852 --> 00:12:20,853
What's going on? Who are you?

111
00:12:20,888 --> 00:12:22,086
It's the Tax Office.

112
00:12:22,121 --> 00:12:24,282
And my name is Chen. Han-Sheng Chen.

113
00:12:24,624 --> 00:12:25,784
Han-Sheng Chen?

114
00:12:26,225 --> 00:12:27,658
Call me Jack, why don't you.

115
00:12:29,729 --> 00:12:32,425
So, why were they going to kill you?

116
