The Japs usually leave
British nationals alone.

117
00:12:35,635 --> 00:12:37,904
- I saw something I shouldn't have.
- Got it.

118
00:12:37,939 --> 00:12:39,496
I took photographs. They found them.

119
00:12:39,572 --> 00:12:40,630
Oh. No wonder..

120
00:12:41,374 --> 00:12:44,070
Pardon my ignorance, but what
are you doing in the Tax Office?

121
00:12:44,177 --> 00:12:45,591
They're killing people out there.

122
00:12:45,626 --> 00:12:47,005
We are completely outnumbered here.

123
00:12:47,246 --> 00:12:48,613
And the Japs are better armed.

124
00:12:48,648 --> 00:12:51,412
So we are going to fight another day.

125
00:12:52,785 --> 00:12:53,752
Hold this..

126
00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:57,885
But before we go,
we're going to blow up a few buildings.

127
00:12:58,357 --> 00:13:00,158
They are very orderly, the Japanese.

128
00:13:00,193 --> 00:13:02,627
They hate it when we
blow up a city's records.

129
00:13:02,862 --> 00:13:04,853
Let's go out. Hurry..

130
00:13:07,133 --> 00:13:08,100
Thank you.

131
00:13:14,273 --> 00:13:15,297
Wait me out there.

132
00:13:18,978 --> 00:13:20,468
We'll try for the British consulate.

133
00:13:21,314 --> 00:13:23,214
They may be able to
get you out of Nanjing.

134
00:13:24,450 --> 00:13:25,417
You have to leave.

135
00:13:25,918 --> 00:13:27,852
You have to tell the world
what's happening here.

136
00:13:31,290 --> 00:13:32,416
I love this part

137
00:13:42,101 --> 00:13:43,932
Come on. Your friends should be this way.

138
00:13:51,043 --> 00:13:52,510
Take it easy, Daisy.

139
00:13:53,346 --> 00:13:54,479
I have a pass.

140
00:13:54,514 --> 00:13:55,882
I have a pass in my pocket.

141
00:13:55,917 --> 00:13:56,948
Shoot him!

142
00:13:56,983 --> 00:13:58,143
There's nothing we can do.

143
00:14:00,586 --> 00:14:01,746
Shoot him!

144
00:14:02,155 --> 00:14:03,713
You're too reckless, George.

145
00:14:55,741 --> 00:14:58,266
Shoot him.. Shoot him..

146
00:15:00,179 --> 00:15:01,146
Hey..

147
00:15:02,915 --> 00:15:04,576
