It says 'Pig'.

228
00:21:52,691 --> 00:21:54,090
How is it you speak English?

229
00:21:54,426 --> 00:21:56,189
I'm not a peasant like these others.

230
00:21:56,962 --> 00:21:58,190
I am Liu Shi-Kai.

231
00:21:58,731 --> 00:22:00,596
My father is a Government Official.

232
00:22:03,535 --> 00:22:04,729
Hello?

233
00:22:07,172 --> 00:22:10,039
You think I can cook with just a pot?

234
00:22:10,943 --> 00:22:12,103
Come and see..

235
00:22:15,881 --> 00:22:18,247
I have nothing.. look.

236
00:22:20,285 --> 00:22:22,253
All I have is this.

237
