Grown-ups.

238
00:22:34,299 --> 00:22:35,596
Teachers.

239
00:22:36,235 --> 00:22:37,224
Where?

240
00:22:38,270 --> 00:22:40,170
Gone.. all gone.

241
00:22:41,306 --> 00:22:42,830
Do you have any rice?

242
00:23:18,210 --> 00:23:19,507
Get up.

243
00:23:20,512 --> 00:23:21,706
Get up.

244
00:23:32,191 --> 00:23:33,180
Hurry

245
00:23:50,142 --> 00:23:51,131
Who's there?

246
00:24:13,766 --> 00:24:14,798
Miss Lee

247
00:24:14,833 --> 00:24:16,630
The boys have taken the Englishman.

248
00:24:26,478 --> 00:24:28,105
That's enough!

249
00:24:29,681 --> 00:24:31,682
Touch him again..

250
00:24:31,717 --> 00:24:34,709
I'm out of here forever.

251
00:24:35,154 --> 00:24:36,186
She's bluffing.

252
00:24:36,221 --> 00:24:39,748
