why I should be bluffing, Shi-Kai.

253
00:24:52,037 --> 00:24:53,834
Here. Let me take a look at that.

254
00:24:54,273 --> 00:24:56,104
You're the nurse, aren't you? Lee..

255
00:24:56,875 --> 00:24:57,864
Lee Pearson.

256
00:24:58,243 --> 00:24:59,411
How do you do? I'm George -

257
